# Normalize line endings: LF in-repo; Windows-only launchers must stay CRLF on disk
# (cmd.exe misparses LF-only batch files — release-blocker class, do not relax).
* text=auto
*.cmd text eol=crlf
*.bat text eol=crlf
*.ps1 text eol=crlf
*.svg text
*.png binary
*.ico binary
*.xlsx binary
*.docx binary
*.pptx binary
# 第43波(43e 对抗轮·高):构建期拼接要求 src/ 与产物全 LF —— autocrlf=true 的 checkout
# 会把文件转 CRLF,build 的 join('\n') 在拼接点留裸 \n → 混合 EOL 产物 + CI freshness 假阳性。
# 钉死 eol=lf,checkout 层面根除(模板字面量内换行 \n→\r\n 会静默改运行时字符串值)。
*.js text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
